NAME: Stone Frog
DESCRIPTION: A tiny frog made of stone. It is incredibly lifelike. It is a soul's weight heavier than one might expect.

NAME: Ancient Dagger
DESCRIPTION: A dagger covered in rust. The blade is dull. It has indiscernible markings on it.

NAME: Wooden Skull Mask
DESCRIPTION: A mask made of broken wood. It looks as though it was used in a ritual or a party.
